-- Turkey's Akbank says to issue bond worth up to 1 bln euro
-- 
-- Thu Jul 03, 2014 10:43AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, July 3 (Reuters) - Turkish lender Akbank <AKBNK.IS> said on Thursday it planned to issue a covered bond worth up to 1 billion euro ($1.36 billion).

The bank made the announcement in a statement to the Istanbul stock exchange but gave no further details.